title: Star Wars books(200) and Short Stories(120)
description:
I keep seeing Star Wars torrents that state Star Wars Novels complete...but when I look at the  files it&#039;s not complete...there&#039;s always about 100 and that&#039;s it....so I figured I&#039;d put a torrent up with what I have...which is "NOT" complete...but close...Now I have about 200 novels about 120 short stories...there are some missing that I haven&#039;t been able to find...so if anyone can help complete this....PLEASE...make a torrent stating the missing files.
Look at the list below.....
They are in alphabetical order and they are all in text format...I see a lot of people who don&#039;t like .lit or .pdf etc.,...so you can copy and paste or open it in your favorite apps.
Hope you enjoy and hope you find some you didn&#039;t have and please seed.

Striker67ca
